			"heading": "Method 2: pearls and cores",
			"items": [
				{
					"type": "text",
					"content": "On some planets you can find larval cores, albumen pearls or living pearls.\nYou can find the larval cores on the overworld and sometimes in caves. Attention: be very alerted because as soon as you try to pick it up, strange creatures are trying to kill you.\nIn caves you can find orb plants. You can open them and take teir albumen pearl. You can oly stack 5 of them.\nOn planets with water you will stumble across armored clams. When you swim near them they will open themselves and show theyir pearl. Pick it up but dont waste your time! Ass soon as you got the pearl they will close And hurt you.\nYou can sell the pearls and orbs at a trade terminal or refine the larval orb to nanites"
